Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:44.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Found it! It's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hot Springs\NA complete guide to the most popular traditional inns
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:49.12,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:50.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:54.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You open it, Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.08,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:01.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think we did well, so we should be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:03.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,but what are we going to do if they've
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,written something bad about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:05.70,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect score...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:16.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,F-F-F-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:17.82,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Five out of five stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:18.80,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:22.37,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,It's five out of ten stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:23.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 11\NBark at the Night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.51,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.08,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to contact Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.03,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.07,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,If you applied the term "retro,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be too much of a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:42.77,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,It's undeniable that the inn \Nisn't suited for this era,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the meals served are plain and boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:45.96,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.38,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ren is always trying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his best to make \Nthe most delicious meals possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.21,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel frustrated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:56.17,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I was certain we \Ndid everything perfectly that day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.35,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,This discussion ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.99,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, return to your workstations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:02.53,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.48,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.53,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like repeating myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to the person \Nwho wrote that article!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stand for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:24.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:28.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.94,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,B-Beanman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.09,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Madam Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.30,Default,Bean,0000,0000,0000,,At Fukuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:38.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.36,Default,Riji,0000,0000,0000,,All of the inns around the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunosagi Hot Springs \Narea scored poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.60,Default,Riji,0000,0000,0000,,This is an extremely serious situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.90,Default,Riji,0000,0000,0000,,considering how, not too far from Yunosagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something of this scale \Nis being constructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:53.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,8000 yen a night, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to pay them a visit one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The completion of this project \Nwill be a huge blow to Yunosagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.50,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't be competing \Nwith them on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:03.87,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,The quality is what counts-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:06.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And this magazine \Nquestions our quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.96,Default,Riji,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the time to be \Nfighting amongst one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:12.46,Default,Riji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the Yunosagi group \Nneeds to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.03,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Watcha doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.60,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for dragging you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,These will be used in the \NBonbori Festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.51,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Isn't it a pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.78,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,But Grandma's really \Nirritated at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so arguing with her \Nis a bad idea right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:31.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she's irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was given such awful reviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and some huge hotel's being built nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.99,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,But it sounds really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to stay there at least once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yuina...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.09,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I'm calling you "balut."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:53.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the one to blame here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.12,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.29,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fest it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.15,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,"Fest it up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I just made that phrase up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.74,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're so funny, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.25,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,You want a vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.24,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know why the publishers \Ngave us that review.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:23.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a lot of \Ncustomers this weekend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even though I tried calling-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.86,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,That's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.39,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Reviews are supposed to be \Ngiven by others, not by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.10,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:34.65,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're unsatisfied with the review,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.87,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,you need to accept it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,move on, and work to improve yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:42.85,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But it {\i1}is{\i0} wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.81,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,is a much better inn \Nthan any of the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:06:00.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to accept such a review.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.18,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana went looking for a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.06,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,She left a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:13.92,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:15.08,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,talk to the person who gave
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso that crazy review.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.69,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fest it up."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.46,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,What does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.82,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Ohana's Japanese deserves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a five out of ten too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.83,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you've reached Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.13,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.33,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, you've reached Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.67,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.89,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager, a customer who had
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a reservation with us just canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:44.81,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.09,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.34,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,This customer's canceling too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.35,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of that magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.52,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.10,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:06.61,Sign8A,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard so\Nmy wish will come true.\N My wish at the Bonbori Festival.\NFest it up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Fest it up." {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nakochi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:18.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't answer the phone right now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to fest it up. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:27.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to fest it up in order \Nto protect Kissuiso. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:37.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that article was \Nwritten by an editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have anything to do with-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You published it yet you're saying that you have nothing to do with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that irresponsible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So the mass media really is \Nas evil as everyone says?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.09,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world \Nwrote this awful article?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're close! Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:01.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The spawn of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:12.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since \NI've felt this warmth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.12,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:29.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Who would be happy after being \Nbetrayed by a member of their own family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.97,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... you always say such harsh things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.79,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I broke up with him soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.96,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Work is so much more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came back alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.55,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to \Ndo a moonlight flit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:56.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That was the climax \Nof our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say such \Nawful things about your
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,own home without even visiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:13.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Rankings like those are \N caused by unavoidable circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:19.15,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Someone high up wants \NKissuiso to score poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.66,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I just obeyed their \Norders and wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.95,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote that article
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without knowing anything\Nabout how the Kissuiso is doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:32.21,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.09,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Gratin tastes bad once it cools down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.09,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You never think of anyone's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:42.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You never bother discussing \Nanything with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and always make all the \Ndecisions by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:48.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,This article, the moonlight flit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,the time we moved \Nwhen I was in 2nd grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my Christmas present \Nwhen I was in 5th grade...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want a teddy bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted a sticker book!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me one in November!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:05.00,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you \Nstill remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It made me sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:09.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I gave you your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I held it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've always held things in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you went out late at night
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and it was dark and I was afraid to be alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I still didn't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Parents' day at school, \Nthe zoo, the pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:30.94,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I never complained when \Nyou bailed out on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:35.14,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You know you just shifted the \Nsubject to your personal grudge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I never complained because it \Nalways had something to do with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:43.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I held it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:49.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I was holding everything \Nback this whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a job that hurts others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:56.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,All this time... for something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:57.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:04.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've had this job for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:07.17,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I raised you with a job like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:09.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you thought that all my "work" consisted of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something that you could be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.91,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,From your point of view- No,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.87,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,even from my point of view, \Nmy job is full of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But I still work hard for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.15,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:31.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.39,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.82,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, \Nbut I want you to write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, \NI can't put up a correction notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to \Napologize in a magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:43.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,All I'm asking you is \Nfor you to come to Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and write precisely how \Nyou really feel after your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it doesn't \Nget published in a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:51.82,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you realize that \NKissuiso is a wonderful inn, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:52.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:55.76,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Not until you write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you write it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.63,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:28.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realize that my mother's \Na tough opponent. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:33.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've always lost to her up until now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pulling my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't told Ko I'm in town yet. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, that's not why I came to Tokyo. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:02.49,Sign8A,,0000,0000,0000,,To: Ko\NHey Ko, it's Ohana.\NWhat are your plans for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Make this part a bit more provoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.32,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.31,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Matsumae Satsuki, regain your human heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}Wake up!\NRelease your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a11}Unforgivable\Nstaged articles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:26.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.84,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You think she'll give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:35.63,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, she won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:36.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:42.20,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,"Unforgivable," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:45.97,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Just how long do you plan on staying mad at me, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.87,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's already published.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.31,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of my job. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.59,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what "eternity" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll never be forgiven...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:08.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.76,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't lose. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:20.50,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take her back to \NKissuiso no matter what. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Matsumae Satsuki, regain your human heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}Wake up!\NRelease your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a11}Unforgivable\Nstaged articles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:25.94,Sign8A,,0000,0000,0000,,From: Ko\NHey. \NI'm going to be at work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Work... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.45,Sign8A,,0000,0000,0000,,To: Ko\NWork?\N The hauler again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:39.23,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been a while. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:42.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This scenery, this \Nconversation with Ko... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though it hasn't{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even been 6 months since I moved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.12,Sign8A,,0000,0000,0000,,From: Ko\NNah, I'm working at\Nthe huge bookstore\Nin Ikebukuro today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.50,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, Ikebukuro was only \None stop away, after all. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:02.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sign doesn't look \Ngreat right now, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:07.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I should read some difficult \Nbooks to learn difficult words... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.22,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:17.17,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:17.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.46,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.00,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, guys, stop flirting during work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.45,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:31.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.49,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:39.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, you've got the wrong gal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.49,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:41.12,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.64,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:48.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I just happened to drop by!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.65,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,You just happened to drop by Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:50.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.46,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:00.38,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for disturbing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:04.77,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:20.54,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you almost at your limit, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.83,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.39,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally reached puberty, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to Kissuiso, old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:30.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:45.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to receive \Nsympathy from an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.28,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He was cracking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.76,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.24,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you working hard too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:13.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:17.76,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But we also need to show results.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.90,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The customer needs to tell me that I'm working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be the one saying that I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.39,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:31.23,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe that was a bit forward of me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:35.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ko, are you mad at me for \Ncoming here out of the blue? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:38.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's so much I want to tell you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ko, did you grow a bit taller? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:47.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ko, what's your relationship \Nwith that girl from earlier?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ko, do you still like-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going for seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.47,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:03.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't get it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:06.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I come to Tokyo anyway? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:13.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have so many pent up feelings... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:17.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.25,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}still{\i0} do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.75,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,You mixed tea and Coke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I want to drink Coke, but the fizz \Nis too strong for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.26,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose to Coke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been \Nworking at that bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.67,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,About two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:51.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at the store seemed \Nreally friendly with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.94,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're all about \Nthe same age too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.07,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:02.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:08.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.86,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:14.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,"Yeah"? Did she tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:15.34,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:19.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.43,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I told her I couldn't return \Nher feelings, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,"But"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.31,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,But she told me she'd wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's kind of unrequited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to not give \N a proper answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It's rude to not give \Na proper answer." {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He should be saying that to \Nme, not the other way around. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I left his confession unrequited. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:49.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's exactly what I did to him. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:58.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:58.95,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:01.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.43,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.25,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.10,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet you downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:19.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this back before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.43,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,The rain's gotten heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.95,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here. I'll go and buy an umbrella-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:34.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I can buy one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.67,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.57,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:50.85,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to see his back anymore. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're drenched!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:01.33,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:02.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-
